<p>The thing with this new hobby as well, is that it reaffirmed my belief that Physics and maths is super important in anything digital. Whenever terms like “normal”, “focal length”, “fluid simulation” and “particle simulation” are mentioned briefly in tutorials, I am happy because I know that at least 10% of the time I spent studying was useful.</p>

<h2 id="overall--good-progress">Overall — good progress!</h2>

<p>This week was more focused on resting and not really trying to push through an insane amount of progress in my new ventures, so I am glad that I started a few of them off already and to a good start. Next week, I will commit harder. See ya.</p>

